{"title":"Hexo安装并部署到Github","date":"2019-09-20T13:28:56.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Sep 20, 2019","L":"09/20/2019","MM-DD":"09-20"},"link":"Learning/b12f390f50cb","tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["Learning"],"updated":"2021-02-27T13:50:00.966Z","content":"<h1 id=\"简要说明\">简要说明<a title=\"#简要说明\" href=\"#简要说明\"></a></h1>\n<p>这是搭建hexo博客的简要记录，供大家或者自己以后参考。最开始我是使用的github page托管的博客，但是后来发现github在国内使用经常有各种不流畅的现象。因此我最后采用的方案是同时将博客托管到自己的服务器和github，在域名解析时，将国外流量解析到github page，国内的流量就解析到自己的服务器。托管程序采用的是git。</p>\n<h1 id=\"配置本地环境\">配置本地环境<a title=\"#配置本地环境\" href=\"#配置本地环境\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"配置本地node\">配置本地node<a title=\"#配置本地node\" href=\"#配置本地node\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>node下载 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/\" target=\"_blank\">官网下载</a> ;<br>\n<img src=\"../images/1568986136/1.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将安装目录最好设置在其他目录，我设置的D盘；<br>\n<img src=\"../images/1568986136/2.png\" alt=\"image\"><br>\n打开<code>cmd</code>查看node是否安装成功，通过查看版本即可验证；</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">node -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"../images/1568986136/3.png\" alt=\"image\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>配置全局变量<br>\n进入安装目录，创建两个文件夹 <code>node_global</code> 和 <code>node_cache</code>，然后执行</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config set prefix &quot;D:\\programming\\nodejs\\node_global&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config set cache &quot;D:\\programming\\nodejs\\node_cache&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后给电脑新增环境变量 <code>NODE_PATH</code> 和 <code>Path</code>，这两个值都设置为 <code>D:\\programming\\nodejs\\node_global</code><br>\n<img src=\"../images/1568986136/4.png\" alt=\"image\"><br>\n<img src=\"../images/1568986136/5.png\" alt=\"image\"><br>\n<img src=\"../images/1568986136/6.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>安装hexo-cli</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"自定义组件-Modal","link":"Learning/4071501d4be7"},"next":{"title":"Nginx用certbot获取Let's Encrypt SSL证书","link":"Learning/97cad6591dc5"},"plink":"https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/b12f390f50cb/","toc":[{"id":"简要说明","title":"简要说明","index":"1"},{"id":"配置本地环境","title":"配置本地环境","index":"2","children":[{"id":"配置本地node","title":"配置本地node","index":"2.1"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Patrick Jun","link":"<a href=\"https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/b12f390f50cb/\" title=\"Hexo安装并部署到Github\">https://www.zzboy.cn/Learning/b12f390f50cb/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"September 20, 2019"}}